    public abstract class AbstractPluginCachedOptionsFactory<T extends AbstractPluginCachedOptions>
extends AbstractChartsLifecycleListener
implements NativeObjectContainerFactory<T>
    Factory to get the plugin options (form chart, from datasets or from default global ones) related to the plugin.
